  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON : The proposed full width full depth rear extension and provision of a roof top terrace are considered to be harmful to the character and appearance of the host building and the conservation area.  The work will disrupt the character and development pattern of the terrace.  The proposal in this regard is considered to have a unacceptable and fail to comply with PPS5 Planning and the Historic Environment; policies 7.4, 7.6 and 7.8 of the London Plan 2011, policy CS9 of the Islington Core Strategy 2011; the objectives of policies H6 (Garden Land), D4 (Designing in Context), D11 (Extensions and Alterations), D24 (Materials) and D28 (Rear Extensions) of the Islington Unitary Development Plan, part 2.5 of the Islington Urban Design Guide, and paragraph 4.13 of the Arlington Square Conservation Area Design Guidelines."
